quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,105,"Ni khubwatoto khwayishia, ne khubwatoto yekha. Ne shikhwakhuruma halali obe wokhuhana akomwikhoyo, omwikanyilisi."
  17,106,"Ne Ikurani khwayikabula tsimbeka tsikabukhane, kho onyoole okhusomela Abandu khukhuwuluukha, ne khwayishia hatiti hatiti."
  17,107,"Boola mbu: “Muyisubile nohomba mulayisubila tawe. Toto balia bahebwa obumanyi ino nishili, nibasomelwa, bakwitsanga mafumama nibasujuda muno.”"
  17,108,"Ne babolanga mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi nomutswenufu. Toto indache ya Nyasaye wefu Omulesi iliikholekha butswa.”"
  17,109,"Ne bakwitsanga mafumama, nibalila, ne ibametanga obwihotselefu."
  17,110,"Boola mbu: “Musabe Allah (Nyasaye) nohomba musabe Arrahman (owetsimbabaasi muno). Elira liosiliosi liamumulanga, ali nende amera amalayi muno.” Ne olalaama iswala yiyio khubuyoka tawe, ne olaboola mumwoyo kwa hasi tawe, halali tila hakarikari wa ako."
  17,111,"Ne boola mbu: “Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye, ulia ulebukulila omwana tawe, ne abula omusanji khubwami bubwe, ne abula omwitsa khulwobulemefu. Ne mwitsoomie okhwitsoomia okhukhongo muno.”"
  18,1,"Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye, oweshia Eshitabu khumusumba wuwe, ne shiyashikhola okhuba mashiama tawe."
  18,2,"Eshikololofu, kho shikanyilisilie Abandu eshinyasio eshilulu shirulanga khuye, ne shihelesie akomwikhoyo balia basuubilanga, abakholanga ebikhole ebilayi, mbu balinyoola omurungo omulayi."
  18,3,"Bekhalemwo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  18,4,"Ne shikanyilisie balia baboola mbu: “Nyasaye ali nende Omwana.”"